text: Carlskrona IF is a floorball club in the town of Karlskrona in Sweden. It was established in 1988. The men's team played in the Swedish top division during the 1990's. The men's team won a bronze medal at the Swedish national championship playoffs during the 1992-1993 and 1993-1994 seasons. ==References== Category:1988 establishments in Sweden Category:Floorball clubs in Sweden
